1. Task Description
    https://adventofcode.com/2021/day/3

2. Summary:
    2.1 Day 3-1
        Given columns of binary digits, calculate the product of the most/least common digit in decimal form.

3. Example:
    3.1 Day 3-1
        00100
        11110
        10110
        10111
        10101
        01111
        00111
        11100
        10000
        11001
        00010
        01010

        Ans: 10110 * 01001 = 22 * 9 = 198

4. Run the program
    cd AoC_2021_Day_3
    make run

5. Run the tests
    cd AoC_2021_Day_3
    make test
